location.fullValue: Spruce Plan, Bluffs at Young's Creek

data.description: A magnificent 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom ranch-style home nestled on a picturesque pond lot. Step inside & be greeted by stunning engineered flooring that spans the entire house, providing a seamless & elegant look w/o a trace of carpet. The open-concept layout boasts soaring vaulted ceilings. The Kitchen feat. custom offset cabinetry, granite countertops, SS appliances & a center island w/ seating. Large living room w/ gas fireplace & feature wall. Primary bedroom is a tranquil retreat w/ its generous size, ensuite bath & a walk-in closet. 3 other well-proportioned bedrooms provide ample space for family, guests, or even a home office. Located near the serene Branigan wooded trails, this home offers the perfect blend of nature & convenience.
